      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RAPID RETURN (3) used the low draw last time and bounced straight to the lead, turning in front before fading to finish fourth over 1207m at Oaklawn Park (Dirt). Will go forward and is expected to be in the finish. TIZ ANOTHER BUNNY (1) filled yet another minor placing last time when 6 lengths adrift in second over 1207m at Sam Houston Park (Dirt) after being in contention all the way. Drawn for a nice run just off the speed. Suitably placed so anticipating another big run. KOCHAN (5) could only manage fourth when resuming two runs back then improved last start but found one better over 1106m at Sam Houston Park, beaten only half a length after being in the firing line on the turn. Stepping up a level this time but on his best form he is capable of a big performance. JOE BIRDEAUX (6) finished third last time over 1106m at Sam Houston Park (Dirt) when resuming from a spell, beaten 3.5 lengths. Stepping up a level this time but on his best form he is one of the chief contenders.",
